  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "$ 5 billion in revenue for 5 months",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka has earned US $ 5 billion in export earnings in the five months from January to May this year, according to the Export Development Board.",
        "Exports of apparel and textiles, coconut products, electronics and accessories, food, beverages, seafood and ornamental fish grew during the first five months of this year. No growth was shown.",
        "Export earnings in May last year were US $ 891.7 million, up from US $ 980.2 million in the same month last year."
      ],
